{"tid":672303,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【想走的人留不住】尼馬始終心儀皇馬，巴黎難以留人？","createTime":"2018-05-21T01:19:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-21T02:31:04.000Z","uid":11512,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"96a290869204bcec60521611dc26fe76d91dbdcb","tid":672303,"uid":11512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T01:19:32.000Z","msg":"雖然巴黎聖日耳門依然決心留下巴西球星尼馬（Neymar），但來自西班牙的《馬卡報》則指出，這名前巴塞隆拿翼鋒依然相當接近加盟皇家馬德里。<br />\n<br />\n該報稱，無論是尼馬本人，抑或這名巴西國腳的父親，均相當願意推動是次的轉會，皆因在登陸法甲後，尼馬才發現自己仍相當鍾情於西甲發展。據悉，這名PSG翼鋒其實曾經萌生回巢巴塞隆拿的想法，但「地上最強」已沒有容納尼馬的空間，畢竟在此子去夏轉會後，華維迪的球隊已接連簽下奧斯文丹比利和古天奴補充，而法國前鋒基沙文現時亦接近來投。<br />\n<br />\n故此，尼馬欲投皇馬的想法便變得愈見強烈，但當然，聖日耳門毫不打算於今夏放人，並希望於未來的日子裡，繼續重用以尼馬、卡雲尼和麥巴比組成的進攻三叉戟，所以他們並不考慮主動出售該名巴西國腳，除非銀河艦隊能夠提供一份難以拒絕的報價。"},{"pid":"61206c0fc6d962ca5ea80c92b427205d21d0f69d","tid":672303,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T01:24:58.000Z","msg":"叛徒"},{"pid":"f347c22b03cbf8d975ee80fbcb9653f1011563c9","tid":672303,"uid":11512,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T01:31:44.000Z","msg":"想同我朗搶位踢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec67dcd1c70f69fd89512edd6bcf5b602bc0b861","tid":672303,"uid":4180,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T01:34:51.000Z","msg":"巴黎咪撚放啦<br />\n話黎就黎話走就走咪好冇面<br />\n最多攬炒，反正巴黎大把錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e9f678c8c72d22a6cae4a76adb7e1bd4d9a3634","tid":672303,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T01:41:25.000Z","msg":"阿朗批唔批先？"},{"pid":"4935e4f5e935ce3a3abd1282cb4c4667f828dea6","tid":672303,"uid":73340,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T01:44:32.000Z","msg":"用2億踢一季<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d319e25bf0072eb29810e7e962297b40e80cbcb5","tid":672303,"uid":11512,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4935e4f5e935ce3a3abd1282cb4c4667f828dea6","tid":672303,"uid":73340,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T01:44:32.000Z","msg":"用2億踢一季<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T01:46:50.000Z","msg":"用兩億嬴個法甲同歐聯十六郎"},{"pid":"28d4b2991c10600d3cdf32b18006c15643deb4c5","tid":672303,"uid":120715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d319e25bf0072eb29810e7e962297b40e80cbcb5","tid":672303,"uid":11512,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4935e4f5e935ce3a3abd1282cb4c4667f828dea6","tid":672303,"uid":73340,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T01:44:32.000Z","msg":"用2億踢一季<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T01:46:50.000Z","msg":"用兩億嬴個法甲同歐聯十六郎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T02:31:04.000Z","msg":"一季都冇<br />\n你未計佢傷"}]}